        WEB_SITE="https://bitbucket.org/maproom/qmapshack/wiki/Home"
      LICENSE[0]=GPL
         ENTERED=20180724
           SHORT="the next generation of the famous QLandkarte GT application"
cat << EOF
Use QMapShack to plan your next outdoor trip or to visualize and archive all
